content:
Salesforce Summer '24 Release Notes

Automotive Cloud

Diagnose issues, driver safety, and vehicle performance using Data Cloud. Seamlessly visualize metrics and insights from Data Cloud right in your Automotive app.

Data Cloud for Automotive Experiences
Unify customer and vehicle data in Data Cloud, and connect telematics systems to Automotive Cloud.

Supplier Recovery Claims
Streamline the process of raising supplier recovery claims for parts covered by contract terms with suppliers.

Product Service Campaigns for Vehicle and Parts Recalls
Organize product service campaigns to service faulty products, recall defective assets, and manage outreach campaigns at scale.

Automotive Foundational Enhancements
Make the most of additional enhancements in Automotive Cloud. Action Launcher is now available in Experience Cloud, new fields are added to Vehicle and Asset, and users can create quote actions for assets.

New and Enhanced Common Features for Industries

Action Launcher
Business Rules Engine
Context Service
Criteria-Based Search and Filter
Data Processing Engine
List Builder for Data Cloud Segment
Timeline
